Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libllvm20
Description: The Sun Programming Language Compiler
 Sun is a statically compiled programming language optimized with LLVM.
 .
 Features:
  - Fast: Statically compiled and optimized with LLVM
  - Designed for AI: N-D matrices and linear algebra built-in
  - Memory safe: Rust-style borrow checking (in development)
  - Readable: Straightforward syntax for humans and AIs
